Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:02.47,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:05.63,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,我突然有一种不祥的可怕预感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:09.83,Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\fs16\alpha&H66&\an7\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H0075EA&}ACG12调查小队【沉默似金_】抄自【F宅字幕组】\N仅供学习交流，禁止用于任何商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.78,0:00:09.83,Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an2}{\1c&HA86C6F&}Re{\1c&HA9AB4B&}:{\1c&H7D60CC&}小{\1c&H4396E0&}剧场 {\1c&H000000&}其十一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:14.62,Petit,Title,0,0,0,,{\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}小{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}剧场{\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HC4C700&\b1\bord6}⑪{\bord2}{\1c&HBB878E&\3c&HFFFFFF&}那个{\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&HB8B80F&}跟{\1c&HBB878E&\3c&HFFFFFF&}那个{\3c&HFFFFFF&\1c&HB8B80F&}跟(以下略){\1c&H9A7CFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}一起{\1c&H4FB4FF&\3c&HFFFFFF&}结账
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:12.03,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,那么 能拜托你把这些都买下来么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:13.23,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.23,0:00:15.94,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,我的名字是菜月昴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:18.70,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,无知蒙昧 天下不灭的穷光蛋是也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.70,0:00:20.50,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,出口就在那边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.50,0:00:23.41,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,对不起是我错了 其实我身上还是带了钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:25.81,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,一开始就这么说不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:27.56,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,虽然一开始就料到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:31.24,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,不过你一开始就说得这么直接 就算是我也会被吓倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:34.09,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,因为我这不推销东西怎么做买卖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:35.76,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,所以说 你想买什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:38.07,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,就是普通的过来买瓶可乐而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:40.80,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,啊 我也很喜欢碳酸饮料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:43.87,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,那种熟食跟碳酸饮料一起吃下去的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:45.23,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,简直没有比这更棒的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:46.04,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:48.32,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在买熟食还有10％优惠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:54.16,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,真的假的 那给我来份炸鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:57.45,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,我偷偷告诉你个秘密 熟食跟饭团一起买的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.38,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,优惠30円哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.38,0:01:02.83,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,哦说起来饭团 推荐你这个新品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:05.56,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,虽然一直都在努力进货 但是总是很快就卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.66,0:01:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真的是很好运很好运 恰好留了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:10.69,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,好好 这个我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.69,0:01:12.72,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,还有 要是在店里消费800円以上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以抽奖哟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:17.84,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,一般人我不告诉 特别容易中奖 不抽的话可是很亏的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:19.98,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,我是不是应该再补上一包玉米小棒棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:22.14,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,酸酸的东西再配上甜食的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:24.63,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,美味简直无法抵挡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:26.18,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,所以要不再来份冰淇淋怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.18,0:01:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,超级好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.24,0:01:28.38,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,买买买！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:31.59,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,这个啦 这个啦 那个啦 那些啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:34.04,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,总计十万円
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:35.59,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,我到底...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:37.57,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,自己选好要买的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:40.62,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,最后却不付钱的话我们可是很困扰的 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:43.22,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,就算你这么说 我也没有这么多钱啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:45.50,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的便利店么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:47.58,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,又来了个麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,唔？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:50.92,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,凡夫俗子居然在狂妄地买买买么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:53.67,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,不是 那个我回过神来就已经...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:55.66,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,我们店可都是好东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:58.65,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,越是识货的人买的越多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:01.36,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,这样么 也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:03.68,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,姑且就当被你的花言巧语怂恿一次好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:06.32,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,这家店的所有东西都卖给妾身好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:07.20,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,全部！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.37,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:10.36,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,车子跟侍女们就在门外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,尽快装好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.16,Default,Priscilla,0,0,0,,太慢了可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:14.82,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,好好 马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:16.81,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,小兄弟小兄弟你让开点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:18.51,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,诶 商品？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:20.79,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,我们已经没有东西剩下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:22.91,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,都让这位公主大人给买走了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:24.29,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:26.03,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,至少让我买瓶可乐...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:27.22,Default,Anastasia,0,0,0,,啊咧 你是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:28.90,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,连我的存在都...
